curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/10541' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8306-1/SGM8306-2", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8306-1 (single) and SGM8306-2 (dual) are  high speed and high voltage amplifiers. These devices  are well suited for video or communication applications,  where inputs or outputs are exposed externally.  The SGM8306-1/2 are optimized for high voltage  operation from 4.5V to 16V single supply or ±2.25V to  ±8V dual power supplies. These devices provide wide  input common mode voltage range and rail-to-rail  output swing. They consume low quiescent current of  7.8mA per amplifier.  The SGM8306-1/2 are designed for high speed  applications. They offer a -3dB bandwidth of 100MHz, a  small-signal bandwidth of 5.5MHz for -0.1dB gain  flatness, and a high slew rate of 190V/µs.  The SGM8306-1 is available in Green SOT-23-5,  SOIC-8 and MSOP-8 packages. The SGM8306-2 is  available in Green SOIC-8 and MSOP-8 packages.  They are specified over the extended -40℃ to +125℃  temperature range.    "}'
